{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0f0ba11f46","title":"中共中山大学委员会关于詹安泰同志被错划右派分子改正通知书","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5b844b1644","index":0,"year":1979,"month":3,"day":21,"articleId":"0f0ba11f46"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"634a5de908","name":"广东文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d1364c4d0c","type":"title","text":"中共中山大学委员会关于詹安泰同志被错划右派分子改正通知书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"b6a76575af","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央〔1978〕55号文件指示，我们对詹安泰同志1958年4月被划为右派分子进行了复查，认为属于错划，决定给予改正，恢复政治名誉。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"8d710af17a","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共中山大学委员会1979年3月21日","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"5c037b8224","type":"paragraph","text":"此件发给本人、其所属单位及有关亲属各一份，存档两份。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"2eff81ec4c","type":"appellation","text":"中国民主同盟广东省委员会：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"05efa07c96","type":"paragraph","text":"现接中共中山大学委员会来函称：关于詹安泰同志在反右斗争中被划为右派分子的问题，经复查系属错划，已予改正。据此，我盟过去对他相应所作的留盟察看的处分，也应同时撤销。特此通知。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"20d92a1af0","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"8ade16343a","type":"appellation","text":"詹安泰同志家属","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"02889be358","type":"paragraph","text":" 民盟广东省委会机关临时工作组1979年3月28日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"06761fbfa1","type":"paragraph","text":"中山大学","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0f0ba11f46"},{"id":"f0970c686a","type":"appellatio